him, miss Minchin.


298
00:18:09.996 --> 00:18:12.231
I promise I'll do better.

299
00:18:12.232 --> 00:18:13.999
Please?

300
00:18:14.000 --> 00:18:16.135
Lavinia, you may continue.

301
00:18:17.003 --> 00:18:20.005
7 times 8 is 56.

302
00:18:20.006 --> 00:18:24.142
7 times 9 is…63.

303
00:18:24.143 --> 00:18:28.280
7 times 5 is 35.

304
00:18:28.281 --> 00:18:30.882
7 times 6 is 42.

305
00:18:30.883 --> 00:18:33.084
7 times 7 is 49.

306
00:18:33.085 --> 00:18:36.955
Dear papa, I miss you already.

307
00:18:36.956 --> 00:18:40.692
Things are fine,
except I never imagined


308
00:18:40.693 --> 00:18:43.429
there would be
so many rules at school.


309
00:18:43.430 --> 00:18:45.831
I guess they're there
for a purpose,


310
00:18:45.832 --> 00:18:48.567
and I'm trying hard
to obey them,


311
00:18:48.568 --> 00:18:52.205
but I get the feeling
I'm doing something wrong.


312
00:19:09.155 --> 00:19:10.789
Good-bye, father.

313
00:19:10.790 --> 00:19:12.924
John…

314
00:19:12.925 --> 00:19:14.261
my son.

315
00:19:28.575 --> 00:19:31.009
I hope when you read this,

316
00:19:31.010 --> 00:19:32.611
it kindles your heart

317
00:19:32.612 --> 00:19:35.213
and puts a smile on your face.

318
00:19:35.214 --> 00:19:37.215
Papa, I'm so proud of you,

319
00:19:37.216 --> 00:19:39.618
and I think about you
every moment,


320
00:19:39.619 --> 00:19:42.821
and I love you forever…

321
00:19:42.822 --> 00:19:44.557
your Sara.

322
00:19:54.767 --> 00:19:56.768
Aaah! Aaaah! Aah!

323
00:19:56.769 --> 00:19:59.505
Now, now, lottie, you
mustn't get so excited.


324
00:19:59.506 --> 00:20:01.507
