her fair share.


507
00:33:33.152 --> 00:33:35.153
Right, Princess?

508
00:33:35.154 --> 00:33:37.922
I told her that's what you were.

509
00:33:37.923 --> 00:33:39.324
Well, not just me.

510
00:33:39.325 --> 00:33:40.858
All girls are princesses,

511
00:33:40.859 --> 00:33:45.163
even snotty, two-faced
bullies like you, lavinia.


512
00:33:49.000 --> 00:33:50.668
Who wants cake?

513
00:33:50.669 --> 00:33:52.937
I do. I do.
I do.


514
00:33:52.938 --> 00:33:54.805
I get the top!

515
00:33:54.806 --> 00:33:56.207
I get that one.

516
00:33:56.208 --> 00:33:58.075
Can I get the top?

517
00:33:58.076 --> 00:34:00.779
Here, lavinia,
you get a big piece.


518
00:34:13.892 --> 00:34:15.092
Miss Minchin?

519
00:34:15.093 --> 00:34:17.094
Yes. May I help you?

520
00:34:17.095 --> 00:34:19.797
I'm Mr. barrow…

521
00:34:19.798 --> 00:34:21.699
Captain Crewe's solicitor.

522
00:34:21.700 --> 00:34:23.668
Oh. Oh, yes.

523
00:34:23.669 --> 00:34:25.137
Do come in.

524
00:34:28.207 --> 00:34:30.641
We're just celebrating
little Sara's birthday.


525
00:34:30.642 --> 00:34:32.710
May I speak to you in private?

526
00:34:32.711 --> 00:34:34.712
Oh, yes.
Of course.


527
00:34:34.713 --> 00:34:36.315
Right this way.

528
00:35:09.215 --> 00:35:11.549
May I just say,
Mr. barrow,


529
00:35:11.550 --> 00:35:14.252
that Sara is quite
the favorite around here.


530
00:35:14.253 --> 00:35:15.686
We went to great lengths

531
00:35:15.687 --> 00:35:18.890
to make this
a special day for her.


532
00:35:31.237 --> 00:35:33.871
I'm afraid your check
to us this month


533
00:35:33.872 --> 00:35:35.773
will be rather large.

534
00:35:35.774 --> 00:35:39.644
There will be no check,
miss Minchin.


535
00:35:39.645 --> 00:35:41.347
Excuse me?

536
00:35:58.630 --> 00:35:59.764
Nya nya nya…

537
00:35:59.765 --> 00:36:00.766
oh!

538
00:36:04.536 --> 00:36:05.537
Ha!

539
00:36:08.173 --> 00:36:09.340
Aah!

540
00:36:09.341 --> 00:36:11.277
Ow!
Ooh.


541
00:36:32.731 --> 00:36:34.999
The party is over!

542
00:36:35.000 --> 00:36:36.100
I want everyone

543
00:36:36.101 --> 00:36:36.968
to go to their rooms
this instant.


544
00:36:36.969 --> 00:36:38.135
But, miss Minchin…

