00:59:35.813 --> 00:59:39.548
But then,
a wonderful thing happened.


820
00:59:39.549 --> 00:59:42.686
The gazelle lay down
next to Rama,


821
00:59:42.687 --> 00:59:45.022
giving him his own life.

822
00:59:56.366 --> 00:59:59.235
He is suffering
from acute amnesia,


823
00:59:59.236 --> 01:00:02.571
one of the rare side-effects
of poison gas.


824
01:00:02.572 --> 01:00:04.040
His eyes will heal in time…

825
01:00:04.041 --> 01:00:04.842
no, no, no!

826
01:00:04.843 --> 01:00:06.042
His memory…

827
01:00:06.043 --> 01:00:07.844
who can say?

828
01:00:07.845 --> 01:00:09.646
He's not my son.

829
01:00:11.448 --> 01:00:14.450
