Mr. Randolph.


830
01:00:14.451 --> 01:00:16.452
He was found in severe shock,

831
01:00:16.453 --> 01:00:17.854
with no coat…

832
01:00:17.855 --> 01:00:19.723
no identification.

833
01:00:19.724 --> 01:00:23.126
Since your son was the
only name unaccounted for,


834
01:00:23.127 --> 01:00:25.930
they assumed this must be John.

835
01:00:27.464 --> 01:00:29.333
I am sorry.

836
01:00:38.608 --> 01:00:40.009
All the hoping…

837
01:00:40.010 --> 01:00:42.611
you must think me a fool.

838
01:00:42.612 --> 01:00:45.614
Is it your wish
to be wise, sahib?


839
01:00:45.615 --> 01:00:50.186
I don't know.
I suppose a wise man


840
01:00:50.187 --> 01:00:51.888
wouldn't have come here at all.

841
01:00:51.889 --> 01:00:53.489
But if he had,

842
01:00:53.490 --> 01:00:54.924
he would have looked
more closely


843
01:00:54.925 --> 01:00:57.094
upon the soldier's face.

844
01:00:58.896 --> 01:01:01.097
What would he have seen?

845
01:01:01.098 --> 01:01:02.631
Pain, sahib.

846
01:01:02.632 --> 01:01:06.502
He needs to be cared for.

847
01:01:06.503 --> 01:01:08.504
He's not my responsibility.

848
01:01:08.505 --> 01:01:10.039
A wise man would remember

849
01:01:10.040 --> 01:01:12.909
that this soldier
was in John's regiment.


850
01:01:12.910 --> 01:01:14.443
If his memory returns,

851
01:01:14.444 --> 01:01:18.715
he might tell sahib
what happened to his son.


852
01:01:20.050 --> 01:01:22.251
Perhaps sahib will learn

853
01:01:22.252 --> 01:01:24.888
that John is in British
hospital now,


854
01:01:24.889 --> 01:01:27.891
wishing that a kind man
would take him home…


855
01:01:27.892 --> 01:01:30.494
away from his pain.

856
01:01:34.198 --> 01:01:35.464
If the plumber comes

857
01:01:35.465 --> 01:01:36.565
while I'm at the bank,

858
01:01:36.566 --> 01:01:37.767
show him the problem.

859
01:01:37.768 --> 01:01:39.635
And don't babble
endlessly with the man.


860
01:01:39.636 --> 01:01:41.604
He's paid by the hour, you know.

861
01:01:41.605 --> 01:01:42.972
Oh, and make sure
those Latin tests


862
01:01:42.973 --> 01:01:45.308
