It's all right.

884
01:03:02.152 --> 01:03:04.487
Aah!

885
01:03:05.489 --> 01:03:06.522
Aah!

886
01:03:30.080 --> 01:03:31.814
Sara, come quick!

887
01:03:31.815 --> 01:03:33.951
It's lottie. I think
she's possessed!


888
01:04:04.448 --> 01:04:06.049
I…I got it.

889
01:04:11.121 --> 01:04:14.924
Will you please get
that child under control?


890
01:04:14.925 --> 01:04:17.294
Not to worry.
Everything's fine.


891
01:04:26.603 --> 01:04:27.938
Aah!

892
01:04:30.874 --> 01:04:33.209
I…

893
01:04:33.210 --> 01:04:34.210
I…

894
01:04:34.211 --> 01:04:35.778
