903
01:04:47.091 --> 01:04:48.925
Well, what is it?

904
01:04:50.894 --> 01:04:53.930
I thought I saw a mouse.

905
01:04:58.268 --> 01:04:59.668
Ohh!

906
01:04:59.669 --> 01:05:00.670
Huh?

907
01:05:09.446 --> 01:05:12.049
Aah!

908
01:05:13.850 --> 01:05:15.052
Hello.

909
01:05:20.290 --> 01:05:22.191
<i>♪ La Dee Dee
Dee Dee Dee Dee ♪</i>

910
01:05:22.192 --> 01:05:23.392
<i>♪ La Dee dee… ♪</i>

911
01:05:23.393 --> 01:05:24.061
I swear,

912
01:05:24.061 --> 01:05:24.995
that child has a pact

913
01:05:24.996 --> 01:05:26.529
with Satan to destroy me.

914
01:05:26.530 --> 01:05:28.264
I'm just not cut
out for this job.


915
01:05:28.265 --> 01:05:29.665
I have no Patience for children,

916
01:05:29.666 --> 01:05:32.868
and teaching…all those
horrible facts to remember.


917
01:05:32.869 --> 01:05:35.004
I don't like it at all.

918
01:05:35.005 --> 01:05:37.673
You like Frances,
though, don't you?


919
01:05:37.674 --> 01:05:39.442
